<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>PatrolLink - Real-time Guard Monitoring System</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="/images/logo.png" type="image/x-icon">
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
      color: #e2e8f0;
      line-height: 1.6;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 20px; }
    header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 4rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .subtitle {
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .tagline {
      color: #60a5fa;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .card {
      background: #1e293b;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      border: 1px solid #334155;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    .card-icon {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    p { color: #94a3b8; }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 25px;
      margin-bottom: 50px;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #2563eb;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 5px;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .btn:hover { background: #1d4ed8; }
    .btn-outline {
      background: transparent;
      border: 2px solid #334155;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover { border-color: #60a5fa; }
    .section-title {
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .features {
      margin-bottom: 50px;
    }
    .feature-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 15px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #334155;
    }
    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-right: 15px;
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 40px;
      border-top: 1px solid #334155;
      color: #64748b;
    }
    .status {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #22c55e;
      color: #000;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <div class="logo">🛡️</div>
      <h1>PatrolLink</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Real-time Guard Monitoring & Management System</p>
      <p class="tagline">Keep your security team connected and accountable</p>
      <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <span class="status">🚀 API Live</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">📱</div>
        <h2>Mobile App</h2>
        <p>React Native & Expo app for guards to check in, report incidents, and receive assignments in real-time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">🔌</div>
        <h2>RESTful API</h2>
        <p>Complete backend API built with Express.js and Directus for secure authentication and data management.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">📊</div>
        <h2>Dashboard</h2>
        <p>Admin dashboard for supervisors to monitor guard activity, manage shifts, and view reports.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">🔐</div>
        <h2>Secure Auth</h2>
        <p>JWT-based authentication with phone number verification and role-based access control.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title">Get Started</h2>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
      <a href="/login" class="btn">Login</a>
      <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-outline">Sign Up</a>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title">Quick Links</h2>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 50px;">
      <a href="/documentation" class="btn">📖 API Documentation</a>
      <a href="/api-endpoints" class="btn btn-outline">🔗 API Endpoints</a>
      <a href="/privacy-policy" class="btn btn-outline">🔒 Privacy Policy</a>
      <a href="/terms-of-service" class="btn btn-outline">📄 Terms of Service</a>
    </div>

    <div class="features">
      <h2 class="section-title">Features</h2>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <span class="feature-icon">📍</span>
        <div>
          <strong style="color: #fff;">Real-time Location Tracking</strong>
          <p style="margin: 0;">Track guard positions and ensure coverage</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <span class="feature-icon">📋</span>
        <div>
          <strong style="color: #fff;">Shift Management</strong>
          <p style="margin: 0;">Assign and monitor guard shifts</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <span class="feature-icon">📢</span>
        <div>
          <strong style="color: #fff;">Incident Reporting</strong>
          <p style="margin: 0;">Quick reporting with photos and GPS data</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <span class="feature-icon">🔔</span>
        <div>
          <strong style="color: #fff;">Real-time Notifications</strong>
          <p style="margin: 0;">Instant alerts for emergencies and updates</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
      <p>PatrolLink v1.0.0 | Built with ❤️</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.9rem;">
        Backend: Express.js + PostgreSQL + Directus<br>
        Frontend: React Native + Expo Router
      </p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
